Rating: 4
I loved, loved, loved this! I took other reviewer's advice and added mushrooms and more garlic. I cooked the mushrooms first with red pepper flakes, garlic, and a little butter. Then I added shrimp to the mix (added salt and pepper to the shrimp before adding), and sauteed altogether. I added a lot more garlic then called for. I then continued the recipe as written, although I added 1 cup of wine rather than the 1/2 cup, and didn't bother with the pasta water. I'm making it again tonight and will add broccoli too. This is a keeper!

